data.description: Lovely rambler home within minutes to Lake Anna and marinas. Private neighborhood with no HOA. Home sits back from road on 5 acres. Beautiful wooded lot. Selling "as is" due to updates that may be needed per new homeowners preference. Super location for lake enthusiast, nature lovers, vacation home, new home buyers, investors. Motivated seller. Bring all offers. Thank you!
